WEBVTT

01:32.190 --> 01:34.990
[How dare you!?]

01:35.039 --> 01:38.030
[Episode 30]

01:40.150 --> 01:40.479
You.

01:40.840 --> 01:41.640
Take him away.

01:45.039 --> 01:45.500
And you.

01:47.870 --> 01:48.200
Move!

01:50.120 --> 01:50.580
Get out.

01:52.560 --> 01:53.420
How is it going?

01:53.789 --> 01:54.990
-It's freezing out here.
-This one.

01:54.990 --> 01:55.870
-Come out.
-Take him away.

01:55.870 --> 01:57.509
And you had to come out here
and go through this with us.

01:57.509 --> 01:58.840
Are the higher-ups not planning

01:58.840 --> 02:00.270
to promote you anymore?

02:02.000 --> 02:02.950
Are you blind?

02:02.950 --> 02:04.010
Alright, alright.

02:05.350 --> 02:06.110
Sorry.

02:06.280 --> 02:06.740
And you!

02:09.910 --> 02:10.400
You,

02:10.840 --> 02:11.370
come out.

02:16.190 --> 02:16.990
Take him away!

02:20.280 --> 02:21.079
Take him away!

02:24.310 --> 02:24.750
You!

02:28.360 --> 02:29.090
Take him away

02:29.120 --> 02:29.710
for inspection.

02:29.710 --> 02:30.040
Move.

02:30.910 --> 02:31.240
Move!

02:31.710 --> 02:32.510
Take him away!

02:36.120 --> 02:36.800
Turn around.

02:36.800 --> 02:37.310
What are you doing here?

02:37.310 --> 02:38.370
Search carefully!

02:38.870 --> 02:39.150
You,

02:39.520 --> 02:39.870
go over there!

02:39.870 --> 02:40.730
What's inside?

02:44.430 --> 02:45.030
"Surprise."

02:45.030 --> 02:45.310
You.

02:45.710 --> 02:46.710
-What?
-Come out!

02:46.960 --> 02:47.690
"Surprise."

02:48.150 --> 02:49.079
Speak clearly.

02:49.079 --> 02:49.840
Supplies.

02:50.030 --> 02:50.500
Food!

02:51.630 --> 02:52.370
Alright.

02:52.710 --> 02:53.560
Go do something else.

02:53.560 --> 02:54.760
I'll watch this cart.

02:55.000 --> 02:55.470
You,

02:55.710 --> 02:56.640
-come here.
-Go.

03:01.470 --> 03:02.680
What are you doing?

03:02.750 --> 03:05.410
-Move the supplies out quickly.
-Take him away!

03:09.870 --> 03:11.330
So much trouble every day.

03:15.910 --> 03:16.310
Get in!

03:35.710 --> 03:36.820
Relax. It's me.

03:37.030 --> 03:38.040
Why did you push me?

03:38.040 --> 03:39.800
What rank am I and what rank are you?

03:39.800 --> 03:41.200
Power-abusing wretch.

03:41.280 --> 03:43.010
I've been roughing it outside,

03:43.630 --> 03:45.630
and when I get back I still have to
take crap from you Imperial Guards!

03:45.630 --> 03:46.360
Exactly.

03:46.430 --> 03:48.760
If you don't give us an explanation today,

03:49.360 --> 03:51.620
the Central Army will make you pay for it!

03:51.680 --> 03:52.190
Yeah!

03:52.400 --> 03:52.800
Yeah!

03:52.800 --> 03:54.590
Arresting people for no reason—

03:54.590 --> 03:55.710
what right do you have to do this?

03:55.710 --> 03:56.440
Stand still!

03:57.030 --> 03:58.500
Once Lord Cao finishes the verification...

03:58.500 --> 03:59.000
Listen.

03:59.000 --> 03:59.800
You'll be released!

03:59.800 --> 04:00.930
Since you know how to steal,

04:00.930 --> 04:03.360
you should know
how to do the opposite, right?

04:03.360 --> 04:04.530
What are you doing?

04:21.899 --> 04:23.920
What's taking you so long?

04:24.600 --> 04:26.330
It's too heavy. I can't move it.

04:29.040 --> 04:30.080
You brat!

04:30.160 --> 04:31.310
Don't think I'll go easy on you

04:31.310 --> 04:32.720
just because you're from my hometown.

04:32.720 --> 04:34.260
What are you doing?

04:41.630 --> 04:42.960
Do you know what this is?

04:43.950 --> 04:44.560
I do.

04:45.430 --> 04:46.730
Do you know its power?

04:47.950 --> 04:49.030
I do.

04:49.310 --> 04:50.710
If you dare call for help,

04:51.430 --> 04:52.360
your emperor...

04:52.480 --> 04:54.740
will send you to your death immediately.

04:54.950 --> 04:56.409
I promise it will be grand.

04:57.070 --> 04:57.600
Emperor?

05:07.560 --> 05:09.220
Your Majesty, haven't you...

05:10.750 --> 05:12.100
I have a bad temper

05:12.160 --> 05:13.820
and love killing loud people.

05:14.640 --> 05:15.630
You know that.

05:17.160 --> 05:18.190
I do. I do.

05:20.310 --> 05:22.170
You also shouldn't be this quiet.

05:22.680 --> 05:23.480
Yes, yes.

05:24.800 --> 05:25.390
I mean,

05:25.760 --> 05:27.720
if you ever need me for anything,

05:27.740 --> 05:29.200
I will do everything I can,

05:29.310 --> 05:30.770
even at the cost of my life.

05:37.790 --> 05:39.520
My legs are numb from standing.

05:42.120 --> 05:42.730
Yeah.

05:50.800 --> 05:51.470
Move!

05:53.800 --> 05:54.360
Are you done yet?

05:54.360 --> 05:54.870
Be polite.

05:54.870 --> 05:55.460
Hurry up.

05:56.190 --> 05:57.000
Watch your hands.

05:57.000 --> 05:58.360
It's all orders from above.

05:58.360 --> 05:59.360
Cut us some slack.

06:03.240 --> 06:03.900
Are we done?

06:03.920 --> 06:04.450
Exactly.

06:15.520 --> 06:16.440
Seize him!

06:16.830 --> 06:17.820
This isn't mine!

06:18.320 --> 06:19.380
You're framing me!

06:20.720 --> 06:21.390
Let me go!

06:22.470 --> 06:23.160
Let me go!

06:24.850 --> 06:25.470
Lord Cao,

06:25.870 --> 06:27.070
this was found on him.

06:30.270 --> 06:31.290
Report it to Prince Duan.

06:31.290 --> 06:31.630
Yes!

06:32.130 --> 06:33.270
This isn't mine!

06:33.390 --> 06:34.450
You're framing me!

06:34.480 --> 06:35.520
Tear off his face.

06:39.800 --> 06:40.860
What are you doing?

06:41.270 --> 06:41.940
My Lord,

06:42.270 --> 06:43.920
This person isn't wearing a disguise.

06:43.920 --> 06:44.720
Take him away.

06:45.510 --> 06:46.460
Wait, Lord Cao!

06:50.680 --> 06:51.240
Lord Cao,

06:52.270 --> 06:53.800
what is the meaning of this?

06:53.950 --> 06:55.659
We are investigating spies within the army

06:55.659 --> 06:57.260
under Prince Duan's orders.

06:57.430 --> 06:59.460
We ask for your full cooperation

06:59.490 --> 07:01.820
so that no important matters are delayed.

07:02.160 --> 07:02.690
Lord Cao,

07:04.160 --> 07:05.690
the person you've arrested

07:06.310 --> 07:07.880
is my cousin,

07:08.750 --> 07:10.300
Li Wang, a centurion

07:10.630 --> 07:11.760
of the Central Army.

07:12.800 --> 07:13.490
If you say

07:13.750 --> 07:14.600
he is a spy,

07:15.720 --> 07:17.120
does that make me one too?

07:18.160 --> 07:19.620
Or the whole Central Army?

07:20.160 --> 07:20.630
Or even

07:21.080 --> 07:22.080
the Three Armies?

07:23.950 --> 07:25.010
Deputy General Li,

07:25.040 --> 07:26.360
I never meant that.

07:26.800 --> 07:28.870
It's just that the item found on him

07:29.070 --> 07:31.890
is something used by that demonic consort,
Yu Wanyin.

07:31.890 --> 07:33.720
I'm only bringing him back to ask

07:34.020 --> 07:36.510
a few questions
to avoid any misunderstandings.

07:36.510 --> 07:37.370
Ask questions?

07:38.800 --> 07:39.260
Li Wang!

07:39.360 --> 07:39.770
Here!

07:40.190 --> 07:40.990
Is this yours?

07:41.120 --> 07:41.560
No!

07:42.870 --> 07:43.430
I asked.

07:44.560 --> 07:45.690
He said it's not his.

07:46.040 --> 07:46.500
Well...

07:46.560 --> 07:47.290
Release him.

07:47.560 --> 07:47.950
Release him!

07:47.950 --> 07:48.350
You...

07:48.830 --> 07:49.370
You...

07:49.590 --> 07:50.920
Are you trying to rebel?

08:03.360 --> 08:04.280
It's the Central Army!

08:04.280 --> 08:05.100
I saw it!

08:05.250 --> 08:07.310
It came from the Central Army's side!

08:08.990 --> 08:09.520
Let's go!

08:10.020 --> 08:10.360
Go!

08:11.070 --> 08:12.750
Your Majesty,
you're getting better with guns.

08:12.750 --> 08:13.550
You're wrong.

08:13.800 --> 08:14.730
It's a crossbow.

08:15.400 --> 08:17.630
Nine Heavens Mystical Fire
Sleeve Crossbow.

08:17.630 --> 08:18.560
Mr. Bei named it.

08:18.680 --> 08:20.410
Don't call it by the wrong name.

08:24.740 --> 08:25.270
Let's go!

08:59.600 --> 09:00.060
Flower!

09:00.750 --> 09:01.480
You go first.

09:07.030 --> 09:08.230
Where is His Majesty?

09:08.960 --> 09:09.760
Your Majesty!

09:10.960 --> 09:11.870
Xiahou Dan!

09:14.550 --> 09:15.080
I'm here!

10:07.480 --> 10:10.480
Everyone entering the palace
must be searched again.

10:10.870 --> 10:12.260
Generals,

10:12.790 --> 10:13.920
please understand.

10:14.150 --> 10:15.610
There was never any search

10:15.890 --> 10:17.820
when we entered the palace before.

10:17.870 --> 10:19.910
Now you keep
making things difficult for us.

10:19.910 --> 10:21.710
What exactly is your intention?

10:22.640 --> 10:24.670
I'm only following orders.

10:25.250 --> 10:26.540
Please, generals,

10:26.840 --> 10:27.500
forgive me.

10:28.530 --> 10:29.130
Eunuch An,

10:29.790 --> 10:31.360
it's not that we are being difficult.

10:31.360 --> 10:33.510
After a forced march
of thousands of miles,

10:33.510 --> 10:35.240
the troops are already on edge.

10:35.320 --> 10:37.190
Could you ask Prince Duan to come

10:37.360 --> 10:38.890
and clarify this in person?

10:41.510 --> 10:42.910
If I remember correctly,

10:43.440 --> 10:44.040
Eunuch An,

10:44.750 --> 10:46.550
you serve at His Majesty's side.

10:47.320 --> 10:48.320
Why is it that now,

10:48.600 --> 10:50.200
when Prince Duan is in power,

10:50.550 --> 10:53.750
he still uses the Emperor's old servant
to send messages?

10:54.390 --> 10:56.070
Deputy General Lin, I...

10:56.160 --> 10:57.020
don't quite...

10:57.550 --> 10:59.480
understand what you're implying.

10:59.840 --> 11:00.700
Could it be that

11:01.960 --> 11:04.120
His Highness is being controlled by you?

11:04.120 --> 11:05.960
Report!

11:06.630 --> 11:08.110
The Central Army is staging a rebellion!

11:08.110 --> 11:08.670
What?

11:09.960 --> 11:12.220
The Central Army is staging a rebellion!

11:16.070 --> 11:16.570
What?

11:17.270 --> 11:18.210
What's going on?

11:18.750 --> 11:20.350
What exactly is happening?

11:20.440 --> 11:21.490
Report!

11:22.320 --> 11:23.180
Commander Lei!

11:23.320 --> 11:24.630
The Imperial Guards
asked us to provide support!

11:24.630 --> 11:25.390
Shall we go?

11:26.000 --> 11:26.720
Report!

11:26.930 --> 11:27.840
The Central Army sent a message,

11:27.840 --> 11:28.690
also asking us for help!

11:28.690 --> 11:29.350
Shall we go?

11:30.030 --> 11:30.490
This...

11:30.490 --> 11:31.090
Come on...

11:34.600 --> 11:36.200
How would I know?

11:36.440 --> 11:38.210
Aren't we on the same side?

11:40.440 --> 11:41.860
Commander, what should we do?

11:41.860 --> 11:42.320
Well...

11:42.360 --> 11:42.960
Come here!

11:43.510 --> 11:44.470
Hurry up and go to the Right Army!

11:44.470 --> 11:45.530
See what they say!

11:45.600 --> 11:45.870
Yes!

11:45.870 --> 11:46.870
Hurry! Go, go, go!

11:49.360 --> 11:50.290
His Majesty said

11:50.630 --> 11:51.630
our goal is to put

11:51.870 --> 11:53.360
the situation under control
as quickly as possible

11:53.360 --> 11:54.630
and minimize casualties.

11:54.630 --> 11:55.830
Do you all understand

11:56.080 --> 11:56.750
what to do?

11:56.910 --> 11:57.710
Yes!

11:58.000 --> 11:59.120
Defensive unit, step forward!

11:59.120 --> 11:59.670
Yes!

11:59.870 --> 12:00.730
The rest of you,

12:00.910 --> 12:01.910
grab your weapons

12:02.270 --> 12:03.070
and follow me!

12:03.080 --> 12:03.600
Yes!

12:08.000 --> 12:08.720
Report!

12:09.750 --> 12:10.480
What did the Right Army say?

12:10.480 --> 12:11.200
They said that

12:11.200 --> 12:13.550
since they abandoned us
after getting what they wanted,

12:13.550 --> 12:14.080
we fight!

12:15.410 --> 12:16.300
♪ Who stakes a claim? ♪

12:15.550 --> 12:16.050
Well...

12:16.320 --> 12:16.790
He's right, Commander.

12:16.380 --> 12:18.160
♪ In the end,
whose hands will destiny fall into? ♪

12:18.200 --> 12:19.660
Deputy General Zhou
went into the city alone.

12:18.630 --> 12:19.290
♪ Treading through fire ♪

12:19.370 --> 12:21.120
♪ Who dares to probe these truths? ♪

12:20.440 --> 12:22.370
They're taking advantage
of our lack of leadership!

12:21.330 --> 12:22.790
♪ Relying only on my courage ♪

12:22.810 --> 12:24.220
♪ I roam this world ♪

12:23.270 --> 12:23.930
Commander,

12:24.080 --> 12:25.000
do we fight or not?

12:24.450 --> 12:25.650
♪ Bright light exposes the evil ♪

12:25.120 --> 12:25.790
Which side should we attack?

12:25.710 --> 12:26.340
♪ Let me break through ♪

12:26.410 --> 12:27.550
♪ The gap on this path to the underworld ♪

12:26.480 --> 12:27.600
The Imperial Guards, of course.

12:27.600 --> 12:28.760
♪ Thousands of lights
illuminate layers of mist ♪

12:28.870 --> 12:30.580
♪ Forged in blazing fire,
I steel my bones for battle ♪

12:29.000 --> 12:30.470
Let's fight!

12:30.550 --> 12:32.320
Kill!

12:30.770 --> 12:32.060
♪ Turning the world around,
the empire resounds ♪

12:32.090 --> 12:33.420
♪ In the chaos,
shadows linger in every corner ♪

12:33.640 --> 12:34.930
♪ Truth or lies, the more you hide,
the more it shows ♪

12:34.950 --> 12:36.340
♪ Messages come from all directions,
like a game of hide and seek ♪

12:36.530 --> 12:37.860
♪ Players in the game
wear masks as they clash ♪

12:37.890 --> 12:39.410
♪ Ghostly flames and loyal hearts,
who will load the first shot? ♪

12:39.320 --> 12:44.320
Kill!

12:39.610 --> 12:40.750
♪ Stamping approval in cinnabar ♪

12:40.830 --> 12:42.500
♪ Yet the ink
doesn't always mark the truth ♪

12:42.600 --> 12:43.660
♪ In the rolls of fame ♪

12:43.720 --> 12:45.480
♪ Not all deeds are genuine ♪

12:45.510 --> 12:46.590
♪ Even with
a petition signed by 10,000 people ♪

12:46.610 --> 12:48.260
♪ You may never make it
onto the merit list ♪

12:47.270 --> 12:52.720
Kill!

12:48.350 --> 12:49.450
♪ In the box of merit ♪

12:49.520 --> 12:50.860
♪ It might not be the Bodhisattva's face ♪

12:50.930 --> 12:53.140
♪ What a world,
each step full of schemes ♪

12:53.160 --> 12:55.980
♪ Danger hides everywhere,
and life's like gambling ♪

12:53.910 --> 12:59.030
Kill!

12:55.550 --> 12:56.620
[Capital of Xia]

12:56.220 --> 12:58.930
♪ See through the tricks,
truth and lies entwine ♪

12:59.130 --> 13:01.920
♪ Betting on black or white,
what harm if you bet right? ♪

13:02.090 --> 13:04.760
♪ What a Jianghu,
every blade cuts the heart ♪

13:04.960 --> 13:07.650
♪ Every move a chain, and each may fail ♪

13:07.770 --> 13:10.590
♪ Unmask this half-true,
half-false disguise ♪

13:10.740 --> 13:15.470
♪ In this game within a game,
you and I are both in line ♪

13:14.260 --> 13:15.790
[Capital of Xia]

13:17.520 --> 13:18.510
♪ For every pure thought ♪

13:18.600 --> 13:20.400
♪ There are as many
who trade their conscience blind ♪

13:20.420 --> 13:21.500
♪ For every loyal and righteous heart ♪

13:21.550 --> 13:23.150
♪ There are as many stained hands ♪

13:23.230 --> 13:24.330
♪ Firearms blaze, piercing the sky ♪

13:24.350 --> 13:25.810
♪ Divine machines break armor,
soaring high ♪

13:26.030 --> 13:27.500
♪ Life-and-death contracts,
countless in sight ♪

13:27.520 --> 13:28.770
♪ Secret orders arrive,
just a few echoes in the night ♪

13:28.930 --> 13:30.090
♪ False or true, good and evil mix ♪

13:30.110 --> 13:31.600
♪ Who will break through
the wheel of reincarnate tricks? ♪

13:31.620 --> 13:33.080
♪ Power and schemes are execution
grounds for tens of thousands ♪

13:33.100 --> 13:34.290
