16:14.720 --> 16:16.170
His Majesty is here!

16:16.510 --> 16:18.170
Surrender now!

16:18.960 --> 16:20.580
His Majesty is here!

16:20.750 --> 16:22.440
Surrender now!

16:24.000 --> 16:24.730
His Majesty?

16:25.550 --> 16:27.670
Isn't His Majesty dead?

16:29.120 --> 16:29.820
So...

16:30.030 --> 16:32.380
So it's the Right Army
who's staging the rebellion!

16:32.380 --> 16:32.910
No!

16:34.430 --> 16:36.690
If that's really the Emperor and Empress,

16:36.690 --> 16:37.260
then

16:38.020 --> 16:39.330
we'll be the rebels.

16:39.360 --> 16:40.920
His Majesty has passed away!

16:40.920 --> 16:41.440
They...

16:41.730 --> 16:43.990
must be imposters sent by the Right Army!

16:44.800 --> 16:45.600
Your Majesty.

16:47.260 --> 16:48.450
At a time like this,

16:49.320 --> 16:51.620
you should show yourself

16:52.210 --> 16:54.270
to display your imperial authority.

16:57.130 --> 16:59.880
I've never seen such a shameless person!

17:00.950 --> 17:02.420
A crippled dog,

17:03.440 --> 17:05.150
daring to stand before my army

17:05.750 --> 17:07.010
and bark madly!

17:12.510 --> 17:13.940
Xiahou Bo, the traitor,

17:14.010 --> 17:15.829
[Capital of Xia]

17:14.390 --> 17:16.349
intended to murder
the Emperor and Empress!

17:16.349 --> 17:16.900
Now that

17:17.720 --> 17:19.319
the truth has been revealed,

17:19.900 --> 17:21.430
he deserves to be executed!

17:21.740 --> 17:22.609
Since you all

17:23.369 --> 17:24.829
were unaware of the truth,

17:26.359 --> 17:27.109
today,

17:28.349 --> 17:30.410
those who switch sides and surrender

17:30.890 --> 17:32.430
will not be punished!

17:33.030 --> 17:34.620
His Majesty is here!

17:34.880 --> 17:36.400
Surrender now!

17:36.790 --> 17:38.400
His Majesty is here!

17:38.840 --> 17:40.440
Surrender now!

17:41.400 --> 17:43.000
-His Majesty is here!
-I, Deputy General Li Zhong

17:43.000 --> 17:44.750
-Surrender now!
-of the Central Army,

17:44.750 --> 17:48.590
-His Majesty is here! Surrender now!
-pay respects to Your Majesty!

17:48.590 --> 17:50.090
His Majesty is here!

17:50.360 --> 17:51.820
Surrender now!

17:52.310 --> 17:53.920
His Majesty is here!

17:53.960 --> 17:55.700
Surrender now!

18:01.020 --> 18:05.540
Long live the Emperor!

18:05.960 --> 18:10.310
Long live the Emperor!

18:10.640 --> 18:14.990
Long live the Emperor!

18:16.460 --> 18:19.380
[Memorial Tablet of Emperor Xiaohewen
of Great Xia]

18:22.200 --> 18:23.060
Your Highness!

18:24.240 --> 18:25.100
Your Highness!

18:27.310 --> 18:28.450
I just received word

18:28.830 --> 18:30.440
that the Emperor and Empress Yu

18:30.440 --> 18:32.350
have taken control of the Three Armies.

18:32.350 --> 18:33.950
Lord Jia and Lord Cao have...

18:37.200 --> 18:37.770
Now,

18:38.200 --> 18:40.800
the Right Army
has surrounded the bedchamber.

18:41.400 --> 18:42.460
They are armed with

18:42.590 --> 18:44.120
a large number of firearms.

18:44.960 --> 18:45.420
This...

18:47.160 --> 18:48.020
Your Highness,

18:48.400 --> 18:49.560
hear me out.

18:49.920 --> 18:52.400
Where there is life, there is hope.

18:52.640 --> 18:53.180
Let's...

18:54.790 --> 18:55.750
surrender.

19:00.200 --> 19:01.480
S-Surrender?

19:04.650 --> 19:07.000
Why do you still not understand?

19:08.790 --> 19:10.000
Everything I've done

19:10.000 --> 19:11.910
is for the future of Great Xia.

19:17.110 --> 19:19.240
The victor is king, the loser a bandit.

19:20.160 --> 19:21.550
It is the will of Heaven.

19:23.880 --> 19:24.640
At worst,

19:26.520 --> 19:28.160
I will die.

19:30.920 --> 19:32.200
Luckily,

19:34.860 --> 19:37.310
I have you guys to accompany me.

19:38.030 --> 19:38.790
Minister Yu,

19:39.640 --> 19:42.280
you really raised a good daughter.

19:44.350 --> 19:45.350
Mother...

19:47.310 --> 19:47.880
Medic!

19:48.240 --> 19:48.570
Here!

19:50.110 --> 19:51.840
Take him and tend to his wounds!

19:56.030 --> 19:56.830
Your Majesty!

19:57.440 --> 19:57.830
We

19:58.070 --> 19:59.350
were deceived by Prince Duan

19:59.350 --> 20:00.410
and deserve death!

20:00.920 --> 20:02.510
I am determined to lead the Central Army

20:02.510 --> 20:03.960
and swear loyalty to you to the death!

20:03.960 --> 20:05.680
And I am determined to lead the Left Army

20:05.680 --> 20:06.680
to redeem myself,

20:06.830 --> 20:08.360
and swear to serve Great Xia

20:09.000 --> 20:10.130
with all my loyalty!

20:10.440 --> 20:12.100
I will not pursue past wrongs.

20:13.590 --> 20:14.590
But from today on,

20:15.480 --> 20:18.010
the swords and spears
of Great Xia's soldiers

20:18.270 --> 20:20.470
must only be aimed at invading enemies,

20:21.310 --> 20:22.240
not used as tools

20:22.790 --> 20:24.520
for treachery and power plays.

20:24.670 --> 20:26.480
Your Majesty, you are magnanimous.

20:26.480 --> 20:28.400
We are willing to shed
our blood and give our lives

20:28.400 --> 20:29.730
to live up to your trust!

20:30.200 --> 20:31.000
Your Majesty,

20:31.350 --> 20:32.830
the Central Army
has suffered heavy casualties.

20:32.830 --> 20:34.310
The Left Army's losses are lighter,

20:34.310 --> 20:35.310
but many soldiers

20:35.350 --> 20:37.200
were shaken during the battle just now.

20:37.200 --> 20:40.030
As for how the two armies
should be settled going forward,

20:40.030 --> 20:41.630
we await your instructions.

20:42.080 --> 20:44.540
The Commander-in-Chief of the Three Armies

20:45.270 --> 20:46.330
is now the Empress.

20:49.160 --> 20:50.690
It depends on her decision.

20:58.890 --> 20:59.620
General Lei,

21:00.720 --> 21:03.160
report the Left Army's casualties
as soon as possible.

21:03.160 --> 21:03.790
If needed,

21:04.270 --> 21:05.830
you can ask the Right Army for assistance.

21:05.830 --> 21:06.440
Yes!

21:06.920 --> 21:07.580
General Li,

21:08.000 --> 21:09.400
the Central Army's morale is unstable.

21:09.400 --> 21:11.130
You must come up with a solution quickly.

21:11.130 --> 21:12.990
If this affects border security,

21:13.000 --> 21:14.480
I will hold you responsible.

21:14.480 --> 21:14.910
Yes!

21:15.270 --> 21:17.440
Generals,
set up camp outside the city immediately

21:17.440 --> 21:19.350
and ensure the soldiers
are properly reassured.

21:19.350 --> 21:20.480
Yes, Your Highness!

21:20.510 --> 21:20.790
Yes!

21:27.070 --> 21:27.870
Your Majesty!

21:31.310 --> 21:32.000
Your Majesty,

21:32.000 --> 21:32.860
Your Highness.

21:32.900 --> 21:34.640
Prince Duan
is hiding in Your Majesty's bedchamber.

21:34.640 --> 21:36.160
He's holding the Crown Prince
and the Imperial Father-in-law's family

21:36.160 --> 21:36.890
as hostages.

21:37.350 --> 21:39.410
General Lin dares not act recklessly

21:39.610 --> 21:41.350
and asked me to seek your approval

21:41.350 --> 21:41.950
on whether

21:42.070 --> 21:43.200
we can take that shortcut

21:43.200 --> 21:44.350
straight into the palace.

21:44.350 --> 21:44.720
Do it.

21:45.070 --> 21:45.490
Yes!

21:50.590 --> 21:51.440
Pack up.

21:52.000 --> 21:53.130
It's time to go home,

21:53.880 --> 21:54.540
my Empress.

22:24.100 --> 22:25.030
This... this...

22:26.390 --> 22:28.460
No wonder Her Majesty could still be seen
in His Majesty's palace

22:28.460 --> 22:30.460
after being sent to the Cold Palace.

22:30.920 --> 22:31.830
Turns out there's

22:31.830 --> 22:33.830
such a spacious secret passage here.

22:33.830 --> 22:34.480
It wasn't

22:35.000 --> 22:36.000
this wide before.

22:52.160 --> 22:53.100
If His Majesty had spared

22:53.100 --> 22:55.590
even a fraction of the care
he gave to Her Majesty,

22:55.590 --> 22:57.310
Prince Duan would have been dead long ago.

22:57.310 --> 22:58.940
We wouldn't have waited until today.

22:58.940 --> 23:01.270
That's why you're still single, General.

23:01.270 --> 23:02.640
You don't understand romance.

23:02.640 --> 23:04.640
Such a shame for that handsome face.

23:04.960 --> 23:06.290
Why are you everywhere?

23:12.070 --> 23:12.640
Huixiao.

23:16.390 --> 23:18.510
Cut off their heads one by one

23:19.440 --> 23:20.680
and put them

23:21.440 --> 23:22.550
right here.

23:25.790 --> 23:26.650
Your Highness,

23:27.110 --> 23:27.900
Huixiao

23:28.400 --> 23:29.200
is gone.

23:38.900 --> 23:41.410
That impostor not only deceived me,

23:43.710 --> 23:46.110
but also killed your only good brother,

23:47.310 --> 23:48.070
Huixiao.

23:51.190 --> 23:52.720
So what are you waiting for?

23:53.480 --> 23:54.310
Do it!

23:54.960 --> 23:55.820
Your Highness!

23:56.680 --> 23:57.540
Your Highness!

23:58.200 --> 23:59.730
Leave my family out of this!

24:00.880 --> 24:02.410
Leave my family out of this!

24:02.550 --> 24:04.080
Leave my family out of this!

24:13.920 --> 24:15.450
Your Highness Prince Duan,

24:15.700 --> 24:16.650
surrender now.

24:18.020 --> 24:19.550
His Majesty is magnanimous

24:19.640 --> 24:20.570
and benevolent.

24:21.230 --> 24:22.630
He might spare your life.

24:25.110 --> 24:26.170
I don't need him...

24:28.400 --> 24:29.880
to spare my life!

24:36.400 --> 24:38.060
Take him to the water dungeon!

24:45.400 --> 24:45.860
This...

24:52.220 --> 24:54.270
Where have you been all day and night?

24:54.270 --> 24:55.070
There's a war going on outside.

24:55.070 --> 24:56.070
Do you want to die?

24:56.400 --> 24:56.750
Yeah.

24:57.030 --> 24:58.830
We woke up and everyone was gone.

24:59.830 --> 25:00.560
Where is Cen?

25:03.070 --> 25:04.340
I took him home.

25:05.030 --> 25:07.710
Cen is sick. Why did he go home?

25:08.960 --> 25:09.820
What happened?

25:14.680 --> 25:16.340
A notice in the city announces

25:17.350 --> 25:20.570
that His Majesty and Her Majesty
have defeated Prince Duan

25:20.570 --> 25:22.170
and returned to the capital.

25:23.240 --> 25:23.700
Really?

25:25.070 --> 25:26.350
That's great news!

25:27.350 --> 25:29.680
I knew my half-baked fortune-telling
was inaccurate.

25:29.680 --> 25:30.830
It kept showing bad omens.

25:30.830 --> 25:31.430
Look at...

25:42.130 --> 25:42.950
Er Lan...

25:46.640 --> 25:47.640
Where is Jintian?

25:47.990 --> 25:48.650
Jintian...

25:49.960 --> 25:50.430
He...

25:55.830 --> 25:58.100
This is the cloak I gave to Cen.

26:01.240 --> 26:01.720
Why?

26:11.050 --> 26:12.130
He entrusted me

26:15.620 --> 26:16.820
to return this to you.

26:50.510 --> 26:51.020
Li?

27:01.130 --> 27:02.390
How could this happen?

27:11.530 --> 27:15.370
[Yongyan Hall]

27:14.350 --> 27:15.070
Your Majesty,

27:15.070 --> 27:15.870
Your Majesty,

27:16.110 --> 27:17.350
you have finally returned.

27:17.350 --> 27:18.030
Thank you

27:19.070 --> 27:20.400
for these past few days.

27:20.590 --> 27:21.880
As long as I can see you

27:21.880 --> 27:22.890
return safely,

27:24.000 --> 27:25.530
I'm willing to do anything.

27:27.480 --> 27:28.680
Where is General Lin?

27:30.350 --> 27:31.210
General Lin...

27:31.510 --> 27:34.370
found the body
Prince Duan used to impersonate you.

27:35.720 --> 27:36.400
So,

27:36.880 --> 27:38.200
Your Majesties,

27:38.920 --> 27:40.920
please go and see it for yourselves.

27:41.160 --> 27:41.690
Alright.

27:42.020 --> 27:48.340
[Yongyan Hall]

27:50.880 --> 27:51.680
Your Majesty.

27:55.550 --> 27:55.880
Your Majesty.

27:55.880 --> 27:56.680
Your Majesty.

28:01.160 --> 28:02.360
I originally planned

28:02.550 --> 28:03.680
to carry the body out

28:04.550 --> 28:06.830
and expose the disguise
in front of everyone

28:06.830 --> 28:08.360
to avoid any future rumors.

28:09.680 --> 28:10.080
But...

28:13.440 --> 28:14.510
after seeing that the mask

28:14.510 --> 28:15.970
had already been removed,

28:16.790 --> 28:18.250
I took a look myself first.

29:13.940 --> 29:15.340
Is this some kind of joke?

29:25.030 --> 29:26.430
Is this some kind of joke?

29:40.200 --> 29:41.030
Mr. Bei,

29:42.350 --> 29:43.830
my head hurts so much.

29:57.590 --> 29:58.240
Mr. Bei,

30:00.230 --> 30:01.760
I want some sweet porridge.

30:03.810 --> 30:04.330
Mr. Bei?

30:17.350 --> 30:18.640
How could this be?

30:19.270 --> 30:20.930
He had clearly left back then.

30:23.350 --> 30:24.200
His martial skills were so high.

30:24.200 --> 30:26.660
How could Prince Duan
possibly capture him?

30:27.650 --> 30:28.500
At first,

30:30.270 --> 30:31.800
I didn't believe it either.

30:32.750 --> 30:33.310
But,

30:34.280 --> 30:36.680
Physician Xiao came and told me something.

30:38.590 --> 30:39.410
Your Majesty,

30:40.180 --> 30:41.310
please hear him out.

30:43.160 --> 30:44.030
That day,

30:44.640 --> 30:47.310
Prince Duan ordered me
to treat someone in prison.

30:47.310 --> 30:49.170
We've used every torture method,

30:49.460 --> 30:51.860
but His Majesty
refuses to write the edict.

30:52.240 --> 30:52.900
How about we

30:53.510 --> 30:55.160
let Physician Xiao take a look?

30:55.160 --> 30:57.420
But when I entered the prison, I found out

30:58.440 --> 31:01.770
that the person Prince Duan
wanted treated was actually...

31:01.790 --> 31:02.590
Your Majesty.

31:15.000 --> 31:15.800
Your Majesty!

31:15.950 --> 31:16.480
Silence!

31:17.350 --> 31:18.720
There is no "Your Majesty" here,

31:18.720 --> 31:19.980
only the late emperor.

31:20.030 --> 31:20.830
Treat him.

31:20.880 --> 31:22.540
His Highness wants him alive.

31:41.090 --> 31:42.260
Physician Xiao...

31:43.220 --> 31:46.350
At that time,
Mr. Bei disguised himself as Your Majesty.

31:46.600 --> 31:48.330
It wasn't just his appearance.

31:48.750 --> 31:51.210
Even his mannerisms
were copied perfectly.

31:52.490 --> 31:53.750
No one in the palace

31:54.280 --> 31:55.600
noticed anything amiss.

31:55.600 --> 31:57.180
Prince Duan
didn't suspect anything either.

31:57.180 --> 31:58.180
It's just that...

31:58.750 --> 31:59.350
What?

32:00.750 --> 32:02.110
It's just that at the time, Mr. Bei

32:02.110 --> 32:03.370
was seriously injured

32:04.030 --> 32:05.290
and on his last breath.

32:05.710 --> 32:06.980
From his pulse,

32:07.000 --> 32:08.600
he had taken a deadly poison.

32:09.720 --> 32:11.320
He was in very bad condition.

32:12.860 --> 32:13.770
Impossible!

32:14.440 --> 32:15.350
When I parted ways with him,

32:15.350 --> 32:17.070
he didn't have a single scratch on him!

32:17.070 --> 32:17.870
Your Majesty.

32:19.030 --> 32:20.290
Mr. Bei's injuries...

32:21.790 --> 32:23.520
were not caused by anyone else.

32:25.070 --> 32:26.660
I'm not her child.

32:27.590 --> 32:29.910
I'm just a lone soul living in this body.

32:30.720 --> 32:32.120
Everything I said before

32:32.790 --> 32:33.750
was a lie.

32:35.010 --> 32:35.740
Dan,

32:48.110 --> 32:49.090
you'll have to

32:49.750 --> 32:51.480
walk the path ahead on your own.

32:52.270 --> 32:53.030
I...

32:53.920 --> 32:55.720
can only accompany you this far.

33:00.130 --> 33:03.460
The only person in the world
who could harm Mr. Bei this badly

33:03.660 --> 33:04.720
was himself.

33:06.170 --> 33:08.230
To avoid revealing any flaws, Mr. Bei

33:08.490 --> 33:09.890
even took a deadly poison

33:10.580 --> 33:13.160
to prevent Prince Duan from
discovering it through his pulse.

33:13.160 --> 33:14.090
So, even though I

33:14.640 --> 33:16.380
did my best,

33:17.830 --> 33:19.170
I could not save him.

33:21.510 --> 33:23.170
No need to bother treating me.

33:23.600 --> 33:24.920
My time is up.

33:25.880 --> 33:26.570
Mr. Bei.

33:27.310 --> 33:28.910
This is how it was meant to be.

33:32.340 --> 33:34.270
I'm already satisfied that I could

33:37.110 --> 33:38.560
buy Dan a few more days.

33:41.670 --> 33:42.110
Dan...

33:48.520 --> 33:49.290
Dan...

33:56.980 --> 33:58.380
I leave Dan's illness...

33:59.630 --> 34:00.530
in your hands.

34:01.640 --> 34:02.900
Mr. Bei, rest assured.

34:06.030 --> 34:08.230
I will do my best.

34:18.590 --> 34:20.719
I still have some internal force left.

34:22.920 --> 34:23.880
Later,

34:25.590 --> 34:27.750
I want to see Xiahou Bo again.

34:29.070 --> 34:29.760
By then,

34:33.010 --> 34:34.600
you must hide far away.

34:41.880 --> 34:43.560
Later, after I left the prison,

34:43.560 --> 34:44.570
I saw Prince Duan

34:45.070 --> 34:46.030
rushing over.

34:46.840 --> 34:48.110
So I found an excuse

34:48.960 --> 34:50.090
to stay for a moment.

34:52.679 --> 34:54.030
Watch out, Your Highness!

34:54.030 --> 34:55.159
But unfortunately,

34:55.710 --> 34:58.210
a secret guard by Prince Duan's side,
named Huixiao,

34:58.210 --> 34:59.670
blocked Mr. Bei's strike.

35:00.940 --> 35:03.200
In the end, he failed to kill Prince Duan.

35:11.720 --> 35:13.250
How could this happen?

35:17.640 --> 35:19.240
How could this happen?

35:26.970 --> 35:27.430
Mr. Bei,

35:32.400 --> 35:33.330
how could you...

35:34.960 --> 35:36.880
He knew I wasn't her son.

35:36.920 --> 35:39.250
Why did he still sacrifice
his life for me?

35:40.560 --> 35:42.800
Mr. Bei had very little to live for.

35:44.780 --> 35:45.990
Perhaps in his heart,

35:48.030 --> 35:49.590
you were already his child,

35:51.820 --> 35:53.620
the family he wanted to protect.

35:55.520 --> 35:57.230
Actually, I returned to the capital

35:57.230 --> 35:58.750
to keep you safe.

35:59.280 --> 36:02.010
But I worried that
you might not need protecting.

36:02.260 --> 36:03.760
Now that we've cleared everything up,

36:03.760 --> 36:05.490
there's no need for more words.

36:06.000 --> 36:06.870
Since Nan

36:06.900 --> 36:07.510
said so,

36:09.400 --> 36:10.750
if I were to abandon you,

36:11.710 --> 36:12.790
who else

36:13.230 --> 36:14.070
in this world

36:14.630 --> 36:15.760
could keep you safe?

36:20.130 --> 36:21.160
Nan's child

36:21.770 --> 36:22.840
is my child too.

36:24.230 --> 36:26.710
I have no family in this world.

36:27.440 --> 36:29.230
The reason I protect you with all my might

36:29.230 --> 36:31.190
is not for any grand cause
of the country or family.

36:31.190 --> 36:33.480
If you dare risk your life again

36:33.480 --> 36:34.680
for this darn throne,

36:35.840 --> 36:37.670
I will tie you up and take you away!

36:37.670 --> 36:38.730
Do you understand?

36:40.510 --> 36:42.400
No!

36:53.480 --> 36:54.590
No. My head hurts.

36:56.840 --> 36:57.640
Your Majesty.

36:57.760 --> 36:58.560
Your Majesty.

37:02.070 --> 37:02.870
What's wrong?

37:04.930 --> 37:05.730
What's wrong?

37:07.330 --> 37:07.670
Your Majesty!

37:07.670 --> 37:07.920
Your Majesty!

37:07.920 --> 37:08.400
Your Majesty!

37:08.400 --> 37:08.670
Your Majesty!

37:08.670 --> 37:09.800
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

37:09.800 --> 37:10.110
Your Majesty!

37:10.110 --> 37:10.910
Your Majesty!

37:11.000 --> 37:11.440
Your Majesty!

37:11.440 --> 37:12.070
Your Majesty!

37:12.070 --> 37:12.800
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

37:12.800 --> 37:13.600
Your Majesty!

37:13.670 --> 37:14.070
Your Majesty!

37:14.070 --> 37:14.480
Your Majesty!

37:14.480 --> 37:15.280
Your Majesty!

37:15.670 --> 37:17.000
Mr. Bei once entrusted me

37:17.000 --> 37:18.000
-to take care of His Majesty
-Your Majesty!

37:18.000 --> 37:20.000
-whenever his illness flared up.
-Your Majesty!

37:20.000 --> 37:20.960
Please go back, Your Majesty!

37:20.960 --> 37:21.760
Your Majesty!

37:22.000 --> 37:22.710
Servants!

37:23.070 --> 37:23.880
Servants!

37:24.670 --> 37:25.470
Your Majesty!

37:26.480 --> 37:26.920
Your Majesty!

37:26.920 --> 37:27.720
Your Majesty!

37:28.510 --> 37:29.050
Your Majesty!

37:29.050 --> 37:30.030
Servants!

37:30.760 --> 37:31.550
Your Majesty!

37:31.550 --> 37:32.350
Your Majesty!

37:33.280 --> 37:34.080
Your Majesty!

37:34.230 --> 37:35.030
Your Majesty!

37:43.230 --> 37:43.800
Er Lan.

37:45.360 --> 37:46.560
You haven't left yet?

37:47.360 --> 37:47.800
I'm...

37:47.960 --> 37:49.090
writing a memorial.

37:49.670 --> 37:51.960
I have an audience
with His Majesty tomorrow,

37:51.960 --> 37:53.030
so I'm organizing my thoughts.

37:53.030 --> 37:54.440
I'm afraid I'll get too excited

37:54.440 --> 37:55.700
and forget something.

37:56.230 --> 37:56.760
So I'm

37:58.110 --> 37:59.190
rewriting it.

38:02.630 --> 38:03.230
Are you...

38:03.710 --> 38:04.640
feeling better?

38:08.920 --> 38:09.710
I'm fine now.

38:10.590 --> 38:11.320
That's good.

38:12.030 --> 38:12.440
Good.

38:13.970 --> 38:15.230
Are... are you hungry?

38:15.880 --> 38:17.140
This is the food I made.

38:17.840 --> 38:18.770
It's still warm.

38:18.800 --> 38:19.730
Why don't you...

38:19.760 --> 38:20.440
try some?

38:23.070 --> 38:24.470
I'll get you chopsticks.

38:25.630 --> 38:26.490
Chopsticks...

38:27.280 --> 38:28.740
Where are the chopsticks?

38:30.350 --> 38:32.480
I'll get... I prepared... I'll get...

38:32.880 --> 38:34.380
I remember I got them.

38:38.440 --> 38:39.170
Chopsticks.

38:45.710 --> 38:46.110
Er Lan,

38:46.670 --> 38:48.110
it's my first time cooking.

38:48.110 --> 38:48.770
I don't know

38:49.150 --> 38:49.950
how it tastes.

38:51.630 --> 38:52.160
Taste...

38:52.440 --> 38:53.500
it for me, will you?

38:58.320 --> 38:58.920
Thank you.

39:12.070 --> 39:12.970
Have you eaten?

39:13.110 --> 39:13.680
I have.

39:20.760 --> 39:21.800
Eat with me.

39:21.960 --> 39:22.840
I'm not hungry.

39:23.280 --> 39:23.760
Eat.

39:31.320 --> 39:32.150
Where is Yang?

39:32.920 --> 39:34.760
He was called away
by the Ministry of Personnel.

39:34.760 --> 39:37.020
I stayed because I was worried about you.

39:40.880 --> 39:41.190
I...

39:42.840 --> 39:44.100
was worried about you.

39:46.440 --> 39:47.320
You know what?

39:47.360 --> 39:49.550
The Ministry of Revenue
doesn't know we're hiding here.

39:49.550 --> 39:52.000
They're probably
searching everywhere for us right now.

39:52.000 --> 39:52.500
They...

40:01.000 --> 40:01.790
Tomorrow,

40:01.880 --> 40:04.140
we're going to see His Majesty together.

40:04.320 --> 40:06.070
We must pull ourselves together.

40:06.070 --> 40:06.470
You...

40:07.250 --> 40:08.510
should eat something.

40:20.670 --> 40:21.320
Cen's...

40:22.710 --> 40:23.710
greatest wish...

40:25.000 --> 40:26.670
was for the people to eat well.

40:28.710 --> 40:30.110
You are one of the people,

40:31.630 --> 40:33.960
and more importantly, you are our friend.

40:37.760 --> 40:38.420
Have a bite.

40:44.110 --> 40:44.710
Thank you.

40:45.840 --> 40:46.670
Eat well.
